---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h1>Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
            <p><em>Last updated: April 21, 2026</em></p>

            <p>
                When you sign in to Ulzii Association using Google, we only store your name, email address, and profile picture in a session cookie that expires after 7 days. We do not store your data in any database.
            </p>

            <h2>How to delete your data</h2>
            <p>To remove any data associated with your Google account:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to your <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Account Permissions</a></li>
                <li>Find <strong>Ulzii Association</strong> in the list</li>
                <li>Click <strong>Remove Access</strong></li>
            </ol>
            <p>This will revoke our app's access. Your session cookie will expire within 7 days, or you can clear it immediately by signing out.</p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:ulziiassociation@gmail.com">ulziiassociation@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    ol {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    a {
        color: inherit;
    }
</style>
